OL,3,CHobbycraft issues recall of craft box
OL,4,Cafter 'traces of asbestos' found
OL,6,FArts and crafts supplier Hobbycraft
OL,7,Fhas issued a recall for one of its DIY
OL,8,Fcraft boxes for children after it
OL,9,Ffound "traces of asbestos".
OL,11,FThe company said in a statement on
OL,12,FTuesday that asbestos was found "in a
OL,13,Flimited number of samples" of the
OL,14,FGiant Box of Craft product, a
OL,15,Fchildren's craft item with 1,000
OL,16,Fpieces.
OL,18,FIt was immediately being removed from
OL,19,Fsale, Hobbycraft said, adding that
OL,20,Fthere was "no evidence of any injury
OL,21,For harm to customers."
