OL,6,F"Product safety is of the utmost
OL,7,Fimportance to Hobbycraft," the
OL,8,Fstatement said.
OL,10,F"Following independent testing of a
OL,11,Fchildren's sand product previously
OL,12,Fsold by Hobbycraft, traces of asbestos
OL,13,Fhave been identified in a limited
OL,14,Fnumber of samples.
OL,16,F"The product was removed from sale
OL,17,Fimmediately after concerns were
OL,18,Fraised, and there is no evidence of
OL,19,Fany injury or harm to customers."
